Comment: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:08.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,{OnScreen}The Masked Actress
Comment: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,{OnScreen Right}Toudou Shimako
Comment: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,{OnScreen Middle}Shimazu Yoshino
Comment: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,{OnScreen Right}Fukuzawa Yumi
Comment: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:34.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,{OnScreen}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The opening ceremony began.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take my eyes off Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Noriko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:20.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko came to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She looked as if nothing had happened during Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She did look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I met her unexpectedly earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:38.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um... And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We greeted each other and then separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:48.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It feels like she's hiding her true self more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if she opened herself up a bit more, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's end this conversation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The tea will begin steeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll announce the plans for January.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:18.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,there'll be a meeting regarding the election of next term's student council members,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:21.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so all second years must attend the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, it's all right if you attend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's all right if you run as a first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just like what Shimako did last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If that happens, it'll be a battle between the White Rose sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That'd be amazing to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then Yoshino-san, Yumi-san and I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:50.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,will just have to go to the election committee's office tomorrow after school, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:58.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,With the formation of a new student council, Onee-sama will finally graduate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:07.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,the meeting for the election of next semester's student council was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please do your best in the election!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We're cheering for you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Those of you who will be attending the meeting, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Could you please let us through?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you leave it until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:46.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay. Tomorrow it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, you're not going to skip school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're quite distrustful of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now then, since the deadline has past,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:05.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you three will be the only candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:11.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In the end, there won't be any changes at the Rose Mansion because it's only us three here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now then, please look at the print out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,First, we'll explain what's written on the page,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,as well as some announcements from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The deadline has already passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Can you take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but the deadline has already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:42.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's one more person that would like to become a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hanae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is there any way you can allow that person to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If all of you are fine with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:01.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, we'll resume the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the handouts in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:36.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We'll explain the contents of the sheets, as well as make some announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.76,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.97,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Why? {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko is running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She never told me anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was surpised as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Your form is splendidly blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really! That Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right. We should calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:02.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and think about what Touko is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to know what you think, as her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Whether it's harassment or insinuation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:20.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Both of them are bad, but I think it has to do with her attention towards Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's because I presented my rosary to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, don't think of that as a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Plus, elections are fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan shouldn't be interested in becoming a serious candidate, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We don't know that for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:43.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If Touko-chan is elected, it means that one of us won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:46.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san, are you saying that you'll forgive her for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it's not our right to be elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying if it's our right or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:57.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to be separated from the friends that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm certainly self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:11.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Aren't the things important to us obvious just from the words we speak so emotionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:17.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can say things out of consideration for others like you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san, that's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,From now on, please tell us your opinions straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,U-Uh... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It'd become lonely if the three of them were to stop getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It really would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They'd become a good group of Roses, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else we should be aware of about Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:10.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah! I heard that she wanted to become a Rose from our classmates.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If so, she didn't have to turn down Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:20.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But if she hadn't, she would've become someone close to Rosa Chinensis! {timing error}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then why did she turn her down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe she would hate it if she became my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko doesn't hate you, Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:35.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She's right. Touko-chan might have her own reasons for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to wait and see for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:51.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did Touko-chan become a candidate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did she want to become a Rose that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Or is she unsatisfied about the current student council for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:07.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I'm a candidate, I'll have to compete with Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That story about first year Matsudaira Touko-san from the Camellia class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Surprising, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Isn't it troublesome for the Roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Matsudaira-san, you're a candidate in the election for the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is there some sort of problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:44.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A lot of things have happened from Christmas until now, but isn't this all for one reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:49.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-san, you say difficult things sometimes, so I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Stop playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:11:02.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But even if what you're saying is true, is the answer something I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:08.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just because we're friends, does that mean I have to tell you everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Candidates have to hand in a report during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:29.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I like you. I'm always thinking that I want to be your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But, at the election, that's the one thing I can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I honestly wish from my heart that my Onee-sama is elected to the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll be cheering her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That natural, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was happy that you called me a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're a good person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not as good of one as you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you looking so gloomy over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:20.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:25.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You think you can trick the of eyes of someone like me, who's been following you around since our first year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't get Touko-chan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even I don't get that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After all, she wears a mask the majority of the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You haven't felt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:48.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You know, I think one good thing about you is that you always show an honest face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're bad at acting, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I love that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:59.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But do you think an amateur like you can win when you're standing on the same stage as that grand actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:05.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try to understand her, it's impossible for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If things continue like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:14.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can win if you're unguardedly honest when your opponent is wearing a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh! When I mean win, I don't mean the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:24.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Instead of your thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let me take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:29.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:41.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Make sure you get a good look inside the classroom while we're talking lively to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is Touko-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,First look. We'll talk after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And Rei-chan was really mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Before I got to say anything, she immediately started talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was my first competition on a bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She said she'd look after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:01.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But ten years ago, I was riding properly with training wheels...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:05.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Normal? Is she the same as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Or is she acting weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though we're in the middle of the election...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:21.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama? Yoshino-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:29.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, there's no atmosphere of support for Touko in our class...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Right? Normally they would be supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Does that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko's at fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:39.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When she's asked about the election, she ignores them, or leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If she does that, she won't receive any support.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Touko-chan's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:00.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If it's fine with you, I can be your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're a life saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:07.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Actually, I came to deliver something my daughter forgot, but I don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Which class is your daughter in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,First year-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:16.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, nevermind. Can you take me to the main office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:16.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:21.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Would you like it if your mother came to deliver something you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Especially in front of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I completely understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Election for members of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of the election?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard from my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:49.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This year the current Rosa Gigantea, Rosa Foetida en bouton, and Rosa Chinensis en bouton are candidates, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It seems like my daughter's cheering them on as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:57.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She said, "They're all wonderful, so they'll definitely win!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did someone hide your shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:21.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken. I left my indoor shoes at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you take them home then? {timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just what I expected from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:31.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The reason I had to take them home was because they were dirtied to the point where I had to wash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who would do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's nothing big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As if you're enjoying this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-san, you're reading too deep into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the office. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:55.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you're going to tell the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not. The teacher asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Your mother dropped this off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:09.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She said she noticed you left these in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What a nice mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:27.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then, no matter if we were laughing or crying, the day of the election arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:36.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I didn't know if you were going to drop out, so I was really nervous inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought about doing so the entire time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:43.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I ask why you didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I had the chance to talk to a student's mother who came to our school a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:55.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Her daughter had told her that she was supporting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:02.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Up until now, I've worried about Touko-chan all on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:06.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but I shouldn't forget the people that are supporting us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:11.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I arrived at the conclusion that I couldn't give up, and now I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if you can give a speech the way you talked just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Your expression and the way you talked were fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:33.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We will now begin with the speeches from the candidates seeking election to next year's student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.69,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,What happened to Rei-chan? {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.69,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Sorry! {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:41.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm cheering you on! You'll definitely be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was shaking too, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Got it? It's all right to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no need for you to show people someone who isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:10.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Show everyone in the hall who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Go with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please hug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:22.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I could feel Onee-sama's warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"The role of an older sister is to embrace and protect."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Those words came back to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I am not unsatisfied with the current Yamayuri Council, nor the Roses themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:46.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,However, that doesn't mean that the wind of change is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.97,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan gave a spectacular performance. {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:50.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Boldly, she was able to thoroughly show her conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:57.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san said she would be able to fulfill her promises in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:01.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And Yoshino-san also fascinated everyone that listened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I need to present myself honestly too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And lastly, Fukuzawa Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please give us your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Elections and becoming sisters are similar in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:23.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even now, I still want to make Touko-chan my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:28.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But Touko-chan should choose the path she believes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:34.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't even have to know what that path is, as long as Touko-chan's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My name is Fukuzawa Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Everyone did what they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:20:59.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:17.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We will now be presenting the results of the election for the members of next year's student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next year's student council members will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,these three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:57.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan didn't enter the election out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:01.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Neither was it because she wanted to become a Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:07.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I saw Touko's face the moment the results were released.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:08.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:11.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko's purpose was to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:17.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:29.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, Noriko-chan, your support had a lot of spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:11.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:15.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Please honestly try your best! You'll be fine! I believe in you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:16.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And then, "Fight"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:20.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no way Shimako-san wouldn't power up after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:22.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san's soft smile returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.38,0:24:28.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time: Key holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.75,0:24:32.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I hope Touko can also receive energy and a smile from Yumi-sama.
