Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:14.86,roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}{\pos(158,10)}Shiroi kizu ookiku hiroge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:14.86,english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Open up your pale wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.00,hira,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}宝箱隠しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.00,roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Takarabako kakushi ni ikou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.00,english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}And let's go hide the treasure chest.
